Articles.Content:
Using a modded 1.1.3 install, and the portraits in the bottom right of the screen that show the kerbals and options are currently invisible. And yes, the pod is manned.

Wondering if anyone knows of any mods that can cause this.

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=719790855

Edited July 7, 2016 by plinyvic

19 hours ago, plinyvic said:

What would help is if you posted a list of your mods as well as a log file.
Otherwise, you will get speculation and/or silence.
I managed to figure out the issue. Another mod had added a firespitter dll file, but firespitter itself did as well. I removed a duplicate, and it fixed the issue.
